Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.19,0:00:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在大家都静静睡下的夜晚\Nみんなが寝静まった夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.72,0:01:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十話 愛哭鬼雪希莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.08,0:01:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於新的作戰命令已經頒下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.89,0:01:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅加瑪不得不道格拉那達準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.72,0:02:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還沒有看過阿納海電子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.90,0:02:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很早前我就想去看看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.79,0:02:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就快來吧,當作是餞別\n等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.25,0:02:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,各位人員...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.48,0:02:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯不必說了,大家可以登陸了\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.51,0:02:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太寵手下了\n是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.19,0:02:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.24,0:02:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯的攻擊地球部隊出發了\n我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.38,0:02:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼親自出陣率領\n他們是真的打算奪取地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.21,0:02:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,也不該派亞加瑪去地球阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.50,0:02:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來我再給你\n阿納海建造的新戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.72,0:02:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們只會作邏輯運算\n完全不瞭解對生死與共的船隻之愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.72,0:02:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解又怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.80,0:03:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們只把駕駛員和士兵\n當作下棋的棋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.52,0:03:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是指嘉美尤的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.41,0:03:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肚子好餓,快走吧\n等等阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.73,0:03:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是這次的新人類嗎?\n這是的新人類?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.76,0:03:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待在亞加瑪裏頭生悶氣\n照樣還是追不上莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.43,0:03:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃了一些格拉那達的名產\n增加體力嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.42,0:03:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏的名產嗎?有阿,月面薄餅跟在月球一樣圓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.52,0:03:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄餅本來就是圓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對阿\n不准笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.10,0:03:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是否肚子餓了脾氣變的不好\n是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.01,0:03:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃點東西心情就會變的好一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.29,0:03:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.39,0:03:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太草率了\n你的MS還沒維修完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.78,0:03:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翁先生..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.84,0:03:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來再做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.55,0:03:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這樣是永遠打不倒敵人的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.37,0:03:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒資格說我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以頂嘴!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,住手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.52,0:04:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他不該先出手打人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...\n翁先生也住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.57,0:04:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先出手的是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別吵了,你氣消了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.18,0:04:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們也走了\n幹什麼?艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.14,0:04:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上回去亞加瑪\n比查他們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會被殺死的\n討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.40,0:04:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十歲之前我住在這裏\n可是不記的有這家店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你..是在這裏出生的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.97,0:04:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能的話我想多留一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.86,0:04:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們要去地球這件事\n很令人難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.36,0:04:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最難過的是得和你道別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真會說話,我請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.82,0:04:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.51,0:04:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了 謝謝招待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.37,0:04:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們怎麼來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.72,0:04:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莉,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.45,0:04:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有跟翁先生說你們要出來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩,以我的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.23,0:05:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以你的方式,難道你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.52,0:05:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯\n雪希莉亞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她又犯錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.36,0:05:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夠了,你走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.14,0:05:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.77,0:05:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪希莉亞,有人找你\n在五號桌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.91,0:05:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.11,0:05:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄餅決定好了,你只要決定飲料\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.11,0:05:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莉,好久不見\n你好嗎?怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.87,0:05:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近心裏好怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.29,0:05:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想逃到別的殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.44,0:05:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又想搬家了..\n對,到別的殖民地去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.97,0:05:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點菜吧\n對阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.82,0:05:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要格拉那達月面薄餅\n還有三人份可樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏的可樂不會澀吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.23,0:05:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯?\n你叫特雷斯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.51,0:05:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.01,0:05:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好球 出局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.67,0:05:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是愛哭鬼雪希莉亞\n愛哭鬼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.82,0:06:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯,你自己還不是被叫做\n懦夫特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,懦夫特雷斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.75,0:06:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏太引人注目\n繞到後面去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去跟姐姐說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.57,0:06:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼路,克雷優,你們可以回去了\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.38,0:06:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪會有人在這個地方敬禮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.66,0:06:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們立刻準備出擊\n方便隨時點燃炸藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.47,0:06:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼供餐呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.34,0:06:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點小事自己解決\n亞加瑪是不等人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.43,0:06:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!別敬禮阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.78,0:06:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐\n彼德,你這樣怎麼行呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.45,0:06:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰照顧婆婆阿?\n三段的姐姐在照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.24,0:06:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我帶他過來,她還送我錢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.84,0:06:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說在第六殖民地可以使用\n快回去吧,你還要準備吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.71,0:06:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.99,0:07:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的錢我會再出發前湊齊\n請別取消座位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.07,0:07:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打翁先生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.04,0:07:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要出一萬賦移民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.06,0:07:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由錢人早就逃走了\n你們倆別裝做沒聽見嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.08,0:07:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他先打人的\n捷度,快回去道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.75,0:07:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.81,0:07:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人在奧干很有影響力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是奧干的老大嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.66,0:07:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏可能有敵人的間諜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.68,0:07:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好在這裏吃了\n可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.19,0:07:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去向翁先生道歉阿\n不行,我正在吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.83,0:07:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被迫下船的話\n就不能去就莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.12,0:07:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰叫你吃這麼快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.77,0:07:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.86,0:07:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧\n吞下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.20,0:08:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?要去道歉嗎?\n幹什麼要我主動去道歉阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.01,0:08:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我該怎麼做好呢?\n怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.83,0:08:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有生命危險的\n可是我有家人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.45,0:08:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道,所以...\捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.59,0:08:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.58,0:08:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種事我辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.01,0:08:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去\n你還是得付移民船違約金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.78,0:08:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是迷你攝影機\n拍好地圖回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.82,0:08:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時候我再給你移民船的票與錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.33,0:08:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只要到布朗港自稱是凱蒂\n馬上就能見到人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.82,0:08:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要拍郊區嗎?動作快一點,報酬還會更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想迫使她當間諜\n我們要阻止她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.92,0:08:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在行動是得不到證據的\n要等她行動再揪出他的馬腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.56,0:08:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要陷害特雷斯的朋友?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.24,0:09:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不想讓翁先生對你另眼相看嗎?\n這可是好機會阿,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.82,0:09:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒好嗎?\n還不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八成又再想什麼詭計了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯\n你又在哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.40,0:09:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,今天有急事\n要先回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.68,0:09:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚上再到我家來吧\n你還記的地址吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.26,0:09:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我家還是有點亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.33,0:09:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了?你的臉色很差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.22,0:09:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.45,0:09:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你從以前就是這樣\n有心事時,會拚命隱瞞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.91,0:09:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別隱瞞阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.44,0:09:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.43,0:09:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩份格拉那達名產月面薄餅,快一點\n我也要追加兩客月面薄餅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然很流行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.85,0:09:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你久等了\n是尼路和克雷優阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.23,0:09:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前整我們的兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.45,0:10:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快回到布朗港\n又要挨戈圖的罵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布朗港?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.91,0:10:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然阿,你認為奇襲亞加瑪可能成功嗎?\n竟然連間諜都是外行人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.85,0:10:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇襲亞加瑪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.06,0:10:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來這邊,比查,莫迪\n米莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.24,0:10:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們..你們聽到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.82,0:10:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.91,0:10:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生了什麼事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.17,0:10:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店長\n怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.47,0:10:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,快阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.00,0:10:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好  好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.65,0:10:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣犯規阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.32,0:10:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打架沒什麼不犯規的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.21,0:10:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克雷優,走吧\n好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.13,0:10:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.42,0:10:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別追了\n為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.86,0:10:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先通知亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.47,0:10:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得在他們動手前,破壞他們的詭計\n格拉那達會很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.29,0:10:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!\n追那輛車吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要去亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.51,0:10:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.35,0:10:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.58,0:11:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!你們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.37,0:11:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?\n我也想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.90,0:11:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,道別的餐會也亂七八糟了\n特雷斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.89,0:11:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?\n少囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.65,0:11:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,你趴下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.40,0:11:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腳縮起來阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.71,0:11:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點超越她\n知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.59,0:11:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女的長的不是挺美的\n艾莉比較漂亮阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.44,0:11:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.91,0:11:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個,我想去亞加瑪\n通行證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.02,0:11:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有通行證阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有就不能過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.90,0:11:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏面的人叫我送薄餅進去\n你認識我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.32,0:11:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也有到店裏來吃過\n你是那家店的人,我見過你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.50,0:11:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你,薄餅冷掉\n會妨礙到店的信譽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.94,0:12:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就請亞加瑪的人來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.48,0:12:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的嗎?\n我不知道,我去告訴艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.88,0:12:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了\n我們準備到MS甲板準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.35,0:12:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的不想用比查和莫迪他們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種叛徒不能信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.44,0:12:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們不是叛徒\n更證明他們活力充沛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.03,0:12:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想說他們是新人類?\n他們和嘉美尤關係太遠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.46,0:12:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們的類型不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.23,0:12:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強化人也跟新人類差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.53,0:12:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不贊同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.21,0:12:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個大叔在說什麼阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.34,0:12:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們已經盡力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.70,0:12:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒上過戰場的人是不瞭解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.10,0:13:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我連捷度.桑達都瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.82,0:13:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種只想救妹妹的士兵\n沒必要採用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.81,0:13:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只用為奧干而戰的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.83,0:13:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翁先生\n不必說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.25,0:13:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想救妹妹哪有什麼不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.48,0:13:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道打莫名其妙的戰爭\n比救我妹妹更偉大嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.11,0:13:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.96,0:13:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長你閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.65,0:13:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,我不懂\n我要用我個人的力量救莉娜出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.10,0:13:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你要去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.75,0:13:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄餅?外送薄餅?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.99,0:13:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.96,0:13:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼的?\n怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.72,0:13:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說等一會..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉她...艾莉,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊急鈴聲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.10,0:13:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.86,0:13:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪的人叫你等阿\n薄餅涼了,我在拿過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.84,0:13:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪希莉亞?快追上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.36,0:13:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能從港口出去嗎\n捷度不是為了此事到艦橋了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷射來福槍沒問題,出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.93,0:14:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MK2?誰啊?剛剛才維修完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.44,0:14:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現亞古捷斯的間諜行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.35,0:14:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,間諜?在上面的人是莫迪嗎?\n比查你在駕駛Z高達嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.90,0:14:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不表現一下\n怎麼獲得別人的信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.44,0:14:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉杜艦長知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.33,0:14:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要去攻擊間諜使用的港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.28,0:14:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.60,0:14:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的,打開MS的艙口\n知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.00,0:14:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,以往給你添了不少麻煩\n你要認真干阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.92,0:14:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.96,0:14:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快打開艙口\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.47,0:14:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想開ZZ高達逃走嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.45,0:14:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是一句小孩子不懂事\n就能放過的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.69,0:14:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是要去打敗\n企圖攻擊亞加瑪的間諜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.14,0:14:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要逃的話我自己會離開\n你太看不起人了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.27,0:14:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡說八道\n不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.08,0:14:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是那種只說謊帶走MS的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?嚇到了吧\n才沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說沒嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.04,0:15:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要奪取敵人的艦橋\n一個人救出莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.19,0:15:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,封鎖港口,把他們三個抓起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.78,0:15:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,凱薩,我瞭解狀況了\n艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.50,0:15:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不懂得人是你\n打開港口的艙門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.66,0:15:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必打開了\n港口發出緊急警報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.33,0:15:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS能無條件出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.34,0:15:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,改裝亞加瑪的工作人員,全部停止工作\n為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.46,0:15:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入第二備戰狀態\n開啟主引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.89,0:15:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩子的胡言亂語你也相信\n太孩子氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.12,0:15:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是等候新人類的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.04,0:15:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何卻不相信\n小孩子靈敏的感受性呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.46,0:15:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不認為那個感覺\n正是新人類的開始點嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.68,0:15:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是..\n太無理是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.77,0:15:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達,比查,出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.89,0:15:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好強的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.30,0:15:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先走了..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.42,0:16:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼能把ZZ高達\n控制的那麼好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.97,0:16:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查你也控制得不錯\n我在安多拉玩過很多模擬遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.81,0:16:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勉強還可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.35,0:16:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距離還很遠嗎?比查\n很快就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.11,0:16:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克C隊出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.86,0:16:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒發下出動命令\n叫他們回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.53,0:16:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被敵人發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.21,0:16:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在對亞加瑪發動全面攻擊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.28,0:16:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,必須毫髮無商拿下格拉那達\n不然就無臉見哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是敵人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.21,0:16:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?總共有三架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.13,0:16:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是怎麼發現的\n尼路,克雷優,出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.82,0:17:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,我們會負責的\n負責?負什麼責?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.87,0:17:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由上空攻擊\n讓他們來不及出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.02,0:17:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等,破壞了港口就沒有船可用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再打什麼主意阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被逐出亞加瑪了,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.89,0:17:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我要奪走敵人的船去救莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.30,0:17:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你再猶豫什麼?去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.09,0:17:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪\n只是擦傷而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.26,0:17:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.40,0:17:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼路,壓制著高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.46,0:17:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.00,0:17:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.73,0:17:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大笨蛋,哪有人會開艙口戰鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫他們離遠一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.00,0:17:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們存心破壞港口嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.38,0:17:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照這樣下去,本艦無法上升阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.60,0:18:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找機會出去吧\n你們想全部死在一起嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.03,0:18:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.16,0:18:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休想逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用雷射來福槍也可以打敗你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.66,0:18:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放手阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.80,0:18:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不放,以前你整的我們好慘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.27,0:18:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你破壞格拉那達的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.07,0:18:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來一擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.87,0:18:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手,會壞掉的\n我就是要打壞你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.96,0:18:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.74,0:18:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全都是因為你洩漏了港口的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.35,0:18:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有阿,我連亞加瑪\n再哪一個港口也不曉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.91,0:19:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道亞加瑪在哪裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.12,0:19:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有拍下照片阿\n但上面沒標出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.17,0:19:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就再去照一張回來\n知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我怕...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.33,0:19:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不聽從命令照樣\n會被捲入戰火死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.86,0:19:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會到你家通知連絡辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.06,0:19:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪希莉亞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.88,0:19:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是報仇阿\n最後一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.60,0:19:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.31,0:19:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用激光劍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.73,0:19:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死在這裏的話\n就沒有機會吃到媽媽的料理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.59,0:19:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.14,0:19:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達,你太天真了\n聽到媽媽兩個字就心理動搖阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.83,0:19:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.67,0:19:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該死的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船不會受損吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.94,0:20:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的,捷度,總之幹掉敵人MS吧\n翁先生不會再囉嗦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.57,0:20:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也希望如此,可是他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.72,0:20:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道自己幹了什麼事嗎?\n我打敗了敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.80,0:20:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是偶然,不是你的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.71,0:20:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?你想坐牢嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.54,0:20:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是為你而打的\n不滿的話,你自己去打仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.58,0:20:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也奉陪\n我也是,我也是,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.41,0:20:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.74,0:20:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要怎麼處置這些孩子\n那是你的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.97,0:20:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是請勿忘記,亞加瑪的所有船員\n想法都與這些孩子一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.11,0:20:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.92,0:21:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想逃出這個\n不知何時會有戰爭的鬼地方阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.07,0:21:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擦乾淚水,冷靜下來\n特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.66,0:21:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你堅持非走不可的話,我借錢給你\n不可能的,那筆錢太大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.24,0:21:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯,以前我一哭,你就這樣安慰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.49,0:21:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.57,0:21:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯,你也一起\n跟我到別的殖民星吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.15,0:21:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你留在這裏會死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.77,0:21:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若真的被你敢下船的話\n你怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.59,0:21:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂,我用我的方式救莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.10,0:21:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺好像落荒而逃\n才不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.33,0:22:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯\n各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.10,0:22:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?\n我想讓她心情平靜一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.45,0:22:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回去了\n雪希莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.38,0:22:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行\n為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.40,0:22:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.75,0:22:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯\n雪希莉亞怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.58,0:22:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你來解釋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.79,0:22:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.69,0:22:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.52,0:22:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她...她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.62,0:23:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿著麻煩的東西的話就必須做個了斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.39,0:23:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖給了雪西利亞一個炸彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.07,0:23:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 在真空的宇宙也不能隨意丟棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.34,0:24:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然雪西利亞為了托雷斯在努力 但不能以錯誤的方式努力哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.75,0:24:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快把包包丟掉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.64,0:24:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ 愛哭鬼雪希莉亞 下集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.71,0:24:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是今天的繼續哦

